    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. There are a few tiny signs of love here and there, but nothing that takes away from how great it looks or feels on the road. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
